research_municipality_step.notes: Fulshear, TX operates under a council-manager form of government. The City Council consists of a Mayor elected at-large and five Councilmembers, with one at-large and four from specific districts. One source also indicates the government type as 'Home Rule'. The current elected officials and their roles were identified from the City of Fulshear's official website and the TML City Officials Directory.
